org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.moead

Class MOEADSTM

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.moead.AbstractMOEAD<DoubleSolution>
      • org.uma.jmetal.algorithm.multiobjective.moead.MOEADSTM
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Runnable, Algorithm<List<DoubleSolution>>, DescribedEntity

    public class MOEADSTM
extends AbstractMOEAD<DoubleSolution>
    Class implementing the MOEA/D-STM algorithm described in : K. Li, Q. Zhang, S. Kwong, M. Li and R. Wang, "Stable Matching-Based Selection in Evolutionary Multiobjective Optimization", IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation, 18(6): 909-923, 2014. DOI: 10.1109/TEVC.2013.2293776
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ke Li
    See Also:
